Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.93,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言語 嚥回腹中
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.06,0:03:04.26,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}記憶 鎖在心裡
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.38,0:03:09.16,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}如今只要 回應這振動就好
